            {
              "id": "s86",
              "type": "text",
              "content": "Constitutional AI (CAI) trains models to be helpful, harmless, and honest by having them critique and revise their own outputs against a written \"constitution\" of principles.\n\nThe key insight: instead of relying solely on human feedback for harmful outputs, the AI learns to self-identify and correct problematic responses…",
